AD_VAL_RULE.NAME: SscccinDoctypeSales
AD_VAL_RULE.CODE: C_DocType.DocBaseType IN ('ARI') AND C_DocType.AD_Table_ID IN (SELECT AD_TABLE_ID FROM AD_TABLE WHERE UPPER(TABLENAME)='C_INVOICE') AND C_DocType.GL_Category_ID IN (SELECT GL_Category_ID FROM GL_Category WHERE UPPER(name)='AR INVOICE') AND C_DocType.issotrx='Y'

AD_VAL_RULE.NAME: SscccinDoctypeCreditNotes
AD_VAL_RULE.CODE: C_DocType.DocBaseType IN ('ARC','ARI_RM') AND C_DocType.AD_Table_ID IN (SELECT AD_TABLE_ID FROM AD_TABLE WHERE UPPER(TABLENAME)='C_INVOICE') AND C_DocType.GL_Category_ID IN (SELECT GL_Category_ID FROM GL_Category WHERE UPPER(name)='AR INVOICE') AND ((C_DocType.issotrx='Y' AND C_DocType.Isreversal='Y') OR C_DocType.IsReturn='Y')

AD_VAL_RULE.NAME: SsccinDoctypeReversed
AD_VAL_RULE.CODE: C_DocType.DocBaseType IN ('ARI') AND C_DocType.AD_Table_ID IN (SELECT AD_TABLE_ID FROM AD_TABLE WHERE UPPER(TABLENAME)='C_INVOICE') AND C_DocType.GL_Category_ID IN (SELECT GL_Category_ID FROM GL_Category WHERE UPPER(name)='AR INVOICE') AND C_DocType.issotrx='Y' AND C_DocType.IsReturn='Y'
